### Get all payments (with pagination)
GET http://localhost:8084/api/payments
Accept: application/json

### Get payment by ID
GET http://localhost:8084/api/payments/1
Accept: application/json

### Get payment by transaction ID
GET http://localhost:8084/api/payments/transaction/TXN-a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-ab12-cd34ef567890
Accept: application/json

### Get payments by customer email
GET http://localhost:8084/api/payments/customer/john.doe@example.com
Accept: application/json

### Get payments by status (COMPLETED)
GET http://localhost:8084/api/payments/status/COMPLETED
Accept: application/json

### Create a new payment
POST http://localhost:8084/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "orderId": 6,
  "paidCustomerName": "Michael Scott",
  "paidCustomerEmail": "michael.scott@dundermifflin.com",
  "paymentMethod": "CREDIT_CARD",
  "paymentProvider": "Stripe",
  "cardLastFourDigits": "9876"
}

### Update payment status to FAILED with reason
PATCH http://localhost:8084/api/payments/3/status
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "FAILED",
  "failureReason": "Insufficient funds"
}

### Update payment status to REFUNDED
PATCH http://localhost:8084/api/payments/2/status
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "REFUNDED"
}

### Delete payment
DELETE http://localhost:8084/api/payments/3
Accept: application/json

